name: RodriguezArtt House - Metal Sticker
description: Stuck to objects located all over the world, is a large series of hand drawn metal tape stickers depicting this and similar images. Each house, there to greet anyone that meets their gaze. Many are gone, painted over, or removed and forgotten, but the homes that remain, wish you the best in life and exist to remind us all that home is where the artt is.   #rodriguezartt @rodriguezartt  -  For more RodriguezArtt check out https://linktr.ee/rodriguezartt
